This is //Dark Dealings Theme//, a [[[sigma-9-themes|Sigma-9 theme]]] for the [[[nightfall-hub|NIGHTFALL]]] canon.

It is a revised version of [http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fish-12 Fish^12]'s (deleted) Classy Victoria theme and is a fork of [[[theme:penumbra|Penumbra]]] by [http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte EstrellaYoshte].

Other than that, it borrows elements from [[[theme:penumbra-bhl|Penumbra BHL]]], [[[theme:ad-abyssum|Ad Abyssum Theme]]], [[[theme:placestyle|PLACESTYLE CSS]]] and [[[theme:flopstyle-dark|Flopstyle: DARK]]]; by [http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte EstrellaYoshte], [http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi Yossipossi], [http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/placeholder-mcd Placeholder McD] and [http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops Lt Flops], respectively.

@@ @@
@@ @@
@@ @@
@@ @@
@@ @@

Paste this in your page to get the theme:
> {{@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:dark-dealings]]@@}}
The theme comes integrated with [[[component:centered-header-sigma-9|Centered Header Sigma-9]]] by [http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops Lt Flops] and [[[component:toggle-sidebar|Toggle Sidebar]]] by [http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte EstrellaYoshte].

Check out the sidebar, by the way. [[[theme:dark-dealings#side-bar|(Click me)]]]

